dcterms:description: A controlled dataset comprising 331 pediatric fundus images obtained clinically from 105 subjects from 2011 to 2021. The dataset contains a five-level severity rating for Papilledema.

dcterms:description: A public Vietnamese collection of full-field digital mammography comprising 5,000 four-view examinations with breast-level evaluations. The dataset assesses the Breast Imaging-Reporting and Data System (BI-RADS) for breast level.
